## HTML Injection
- Always sanitize HTML content before rendering

## Secure Local Storage
- Avoid storing tokens in `localStorage` or `sessionStorage`

## CSP Compliance
- Ensure third-party scripts do not violate Content Security Policy

## Dependency Hygiene
- Keep all frontend libraries up-to-date and monitor known vulnerabilities
